title: Small Group Activty - Build a Class Diagram for the Integer Calculator (Baseline) & identify stubs

quizDescription.text:
Purpose of the Activity
The purpose of this exercise is to build a growing understanding of one of the more fundamental UML design diagrams, the Class Diagram.
